      "title": "New Vice-Chancellor appointed to Wayamba University",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Senior Professor J.M.U.K Jayasinghe has been appointed as the new Vice-Chancellor of the Wayamba University.",
        "The letter of appointment was handed over to Prof. Jayasinghe by President Gotabaya Rajapaksa at the President\u2019s House in Colombo today (29), the PMD said."
